The Sophic Society of Assassins have only a single symbol marking one of their order. The Ithari is a poisoned dagger that causes a burning sensation when it touches bare skin, and drains the strength of those who are injured by it. Whoever left this dagger here belonged to one of the most powerful and deadly organizations in Valratha.
